main event: A witness observed a round, large, white object with radiating rays over Houma, Louisiana on December 27, 1965.
interesting points: The object had several smaller objects that detached from it for 1-2 minutes.
The object exhibited high-speed maneuvers and was controlled by 'light rays'.
The witness's father, a licensed pilot, also observed the object.
The object was accompanied by a white vapor or cloud.
Similar objects had been previously sighted in the area.
sighted object: a round, large, white object with radiating rays
